author: Adam Savage’s Tested
description:
Today's build features one of Adam's favorite prop replicas ever: a perfect recreation of the White Witch's staff from The Chronicles of Narnia! But over the years, the ice crystal parts of the prop has broken into multiple pieces. So with some recently-learned UV resin techniques, Adam makes an attempt to fix both ends of this magnificent prop!

Adam Savage Learns Resin Hacks from @EvanAndKatelyn: https://youtu.be/iTIILm_r2Jc
